seller-sku.description: The Seller SKU for the item, which is unique within the seller's inventory.

fulfillment-channel-sku.description: The SKU assigned to the item by the fulfillment network.

asin.description: The unique identifier for the product in the Amazon catalog.

condition-type.description: The condition type of the item, such as 'New', 'Used', or 'Refurbished'.

Warehouse-Condition-code.description: The warehouse code indicating the storage location and condition of the item.

Quantity Available.description: The total quantity of this item available in the fulfillment center.

dataEndTime.description: The end time for the data provided, formatted as a date.
